00:43:58,799 --> 00:44:08,250
Whatever suits you, you should wear, not like 
all the people wearing that Moss Brothers

369
00:44:08,250 --> 00:44:17,990
dress, in the grey suit, horrible-looking, 
and absolutely making clowns out of them.

370
00:44:17,990 --> 00:44:30,809
No clownish things are necessary, no dandy 
stuff is necessary: simple, beautiful dresses

371
00:44:30,809 --> 00:44:37,950
should be worn, which give you dignity.

372
00:44:37,950 --> 00:44:51,329
Actually in the East, people believe that 
God has given you a beautiful body, and it

373
00:44:51,329 --> 00:45:02,730
is to be adorned with the beauty of what human 
beings have created, just to respect it, just

374
00:45:02,730 --> 00:45:05,140
to worship your body.

375
00:45:05,140 --> 00:45:08,960
For example now in India people wear, women 
wear their saris.

376
00:45:08,960 --> 00:45:16,250
The saris are expressive of their moods of 
these women and of expression of their worship

377
00:45:16,250 --> 00:45:20,630
of their body, because you must respect your 
body.

378
00:45:20,630 --> 00:45:37,020
Dresses should be such that should be for 
utility as well as dignity.

379
00:45:37,020 --> 00:45:42,289
There is no need to have uniform clothes for 
Sahaja Yoga at all, you see, I do not like

380
00:45:42,289 --> 00:45:43,289
it.

381
00:45:43,289 --> 00:45:45,359
There should be variety, as the nature is.

382
00:45:45,359 --> 00:45:47,480
Everyone should look a different person.

383
00:45:47,480 --> 00:45:58,450
For a puja and all that you may wear something 
similar, doesn’t matter, where your attention

384
00:45:58,450 --> 00:46:03,390
need not be on the variety, but outside, you 
should be a normal person.

385
00:46:03,390 --> 00:46:10,309
You are all householders, nobody has to announce 
something.

386
00:46:10,309 --> 00:46:14,010
Even you people, I do not tell you that you 
put on your red mark while walking on the

387
00:46:14,010 --> 00:46:18,799
street, because you should be like normal 
people, not to be pointed out.

388
00:46:18,799 --> 00:46:29,530
You need not be absurdly dressed or funnily 
dressed; in a normal way as others wear.

389
00:46:29,530 --> 00:46:42,230
To be normal is very important in Sahaja Yoga.

390
00:46:42,230 --> 00:46:51,171
Then we have to know that Sahaja Yogis have 
to get over all kinds of discrimination and

391
00:46:51,171 --> 00:46:56,960
identifications according to races, color 
or different religions into you are born.

392
00:46:56,960 --> 00:47:06,210
Because you are born as a Christian, you do 
not belong to a church.

393
00:47:06,210 --> 00:47:19,410
You were not born in a church, thank God, 
otherwise all the spirits there would capture

394
00:47:19,410 --> 00:47:21,070
you immediately.

395
00:47:21,070 --> 00:47:26,040
But these identifications will linger on.

396
00:47:26,040 --> 00:47:33,450
To accept anything new, you are to be reborn, 
and you are reborn now.

397
00:47:33,450 --> 00:47:42,380
Now you are dharmatita – means you need 
not follow any particular type of religion.

398
00:47:42,380 --> 00:47:51,940
You are open to all the religions, and all 
the essence of religions you have to take.

399
00:47:51,940 --> 00:47:58,079
You are not to denounce any religion any time, 
to insult any religion any time, or to insult

