00:47:58,079 --> 00:48:07,290
any religious Incarnation at any time: it’s 
sin, it is a great sin in Sahaja Yoga; any

401
00:48:07,290 --> 00:48:19,940
one of them, and you know who they are.

402
00:48:19,940 --> 00:48:23,210
There should be no racial understanding of 
oneself.

403
00:48:23,210 --> 00:48:34,069
You could have been a Chinese or you could 
have been a Negro, you could have been anything.

404
00:48:34,069 --> 00:48:46,539
As long as we are all human beings, we should 
know that we laugh the same way, we smile

405
00:48:46,539 --> 00:48:50,020
the same way, we hold the same way.

406
00:48:50,020 --> 00:49:01,110
This is all conditioned in our mind of this 
society that you, some are untouchables, some

407
00:49:01,110 --> 00:49:10,950
are touchables: this is in our Indian community 
– horrible people.

408
00:49:10,950 --> 00:49:19,849
Brahminism of India has ruined India completely, 
and you learn from them.

409
00:49:19,849 --> 00:49:30,750
For example, who was Vyasa, the one who wrote 
Gita?

410
00:49:30,750 --> 00:49:32,770
Who was he?

411
00:49:32,770 --> 00:49:37,500
He was illegitimate son of a fisherwoman.

412
00:49:37,500 --> 00:49:41,950
That’s why deliberately he was born like 
that.

413
00:49:41,950 --> 00:49:48,470
All these Brahmins who read Gita, tell them 
who was Vyasa?

414
00:49:48,470 --> 00:49:54,200
“Brahmins” are those who are realized 
souls, and for realized souls there’s nothing

415
00:49:54,200 --> 00:50:00,480
like all these nonsensical things, like where 
are you born, in what caste and community

416
00:50:00,480 --> 00:50:02,869
you are born.

