00:50:02,869 --> 00:50:18,690
With all education and everything in the West, 
you find this nonsense of racialism; I just

418
00:50:18,690 --> 00:50:20,790
can’t understand.

419
00:50:20,790 --> 00:50:27,329
If somebody is fair or dark, after all God 
has to make variety, in color, in every way.

420
00:50:27,329 --> 00:50:36,900
Who told you that you are the most handsome 
people going round?

421
00:50:36,900 --> 00:50:51,200
Maybe for some of the markets here, or maybe 
in the Hollywood it may fit in; but in the

422
00:50:51,200 --> 00:51:00,870
kingdom of God all these so-called handsome 
people will be denied entry; marrying seven

