00:51:19,930 --> 00:51:25,049
I mean, people are a little bit aware of it, 
that’s why they go and tan their faces.

427
00:51:25,049 --> 00:51:26,049
I don’t know.

428
00:51:26,049 --> 00:51:43,010
They are quite aware that it is too much showing 
off we are doing.

429
00:51:43,010 --> 00:51:47,130
But to have vanity, to have such absurd ideas!

