00:51:55,070 --> 00:51:56,910
be different types of hair.

432
00:51:56,910 --> 00:52:00,140
And why do you like a particular type of hair?

433
00:52:00,140 --> 00:52:01,720
This I can’t understand.

434
00:52:01,720 --> 00:52:05,660
There’s nothing like “like” and “dislike”, 
whatever God has created is all beautiful.

435
00:52:05,660 --> 00:52:10,539
Who are you to judge whether “I like this” 
and “I like that”?

436
00:52:10,539 --> 00:52:13,010
“I”, who is this “I”?

437
00:52:13,010 --> 00:52:14,990
Who likes is Mr.

438
00:52:14,990 --> 00:52:22,440
Ego, which is being pampered by this society, 
which teaches you how to smoke cigars and

439
00:52:22,440 --> 00:52:26,010
how to have your lager, morning till evening.

440
00:52:26,010 --> 00:52:35,860
All this training and all this conditioning 
has to be thrown away, just like filth, and

441
00:52:35,860 --> 00:52:41,990
see that God has created all of you as His 
own children.

442
00:52:41,990 --> 00:52:45,720
It’s such a beautiful thing!

443
00:52:45,720 --> 00:52:51,799
Why do you want to make it ugly with these 
ugly ideas?

444
00:52:51,799 --> 00:53:02,840
All this ugliness of “I like” and “I 
dislike” are nonsensical.

445
00:53:02,840 --> 00:53:06,720
Only there should be one word: “I love”.

446
00:53:06,720 --> 00:53:08,599
Forget everything.

447
00:53:08,599 --> 00:53:19,089
There’s no need to remember what British 
did to Indians and what Germans did to Jews:

448
00:53:19,089 --> 00:53:20,630
forget it.

449
00:53:20,630 --> 00:53:32,960
Those people who did anything are dead and 
finished; we are different people, we are

450
00:53:32,960 --> 00:53:34,809
different people.

451
00:53:34,809 --> 00:53:37,579
We are saints.

452
00:53:37,579 --> 00:53:48,680
This is for your Statutes, I have told you, 
which you have to imbibe.

453
00:53:48,680 --> 00:54:04,790
But today I authorize you to be the gurus, 
so that through your own character and through

454
00:54:04,790 --> 00:54:16,799
your own personalities, the way you practice 
Sahaja Yoga in your own life and manifest

455
00:54:16,799 --> 00:54:19,930
the light, others will follow you.

456
00:54:19,930 --> 00:54:29,190
And that you will establish the Statutes of 
the Lord in their hearts and emancipate them,

457
00:54:29,190 --> 00:54:35,780
give them their salvation, because you have 
got your salvation.

458
00:54:35,780 --> 00:54:39,160
You are the channels.

459
00:54:39,160 --> 00:54:44,829
Without the channels, this all-pervading Power 
cannot work out, that’s the system.

460
00:54:44,829 --> 00:54:52,460
If you see the sun, its light spreads through 
its rays.

461
00:54:52,460 --> 00:55:03,960
From your heart the blood flows through arteries; 
they become smaller and smaller.

462
00:55:03,960 --> 00:55:13,799
You are the arteries which is going to flow 
this blood of My Love to all the people.

463
00:55:13,799 --> 00:55:19,660
If the arteries are broken, it will not reach 
the people.

464
00:55:19,660 --> 00:55:22,510
That is why you are so important; very, very 
important.

465
00:55:22,510 --> 00:55:35,950
The bigger you become, the bigger artery you 
become, then you encompass more people.

466
00:55:35,950 --> 00:55:40,519
By that also you are more responsible.

467
00:55:40,519 --> 00:55:53,660
Guru must have the dignity, as I have told 
you last time.

468
00:55:53,660 --> 00:55:58,750
“Guru” means the weight, is the gravity.

469
00:55:58,750 --> 00:56:01,549
“Gurutwa” means gravity.

470
00:56:01,549 --> 00:56:06,390
You must have the gravity, by your weight.

471
00:56:06,390 --> 00:56:22,260
“Weight” means the weight of your character, 
weight of your dignity, the weight of your

472
00:56:22,260 --> 00:56:29,592
behavior, the weight of your faiths, and your 
light.

473
00:56:29,592 --> 00:56:49,850
You become the guru not through frivolousness 
and vanity, cheapness, vulgar language, cheap

474
00:56:49,850 --> 00:57:04,730
jokes, anger, temper: all must be avoided 
completely.

475
00:57:04,730 --> 00:57:23,670
With the weight of your sweetness, of your 
tongue, the dignity will attract people, just

476
00:57:23,670 --> 00:57:33,589
like the flowers when loaded with nectar attract 
the bees from all over; in the same way you’ll

477
00:57:33,589 --> 00:57:37,990
be attracting people.

478
00:57:37,990 --> 00:57:46,369
But be proud of that; be very, very proud 
of that, and have sympathies for others and

479
00:57:46,369 --> 00:57:47,630
care for others.

480
00:57:47,630 --> 00:58:03,430
Now in short I have to tell you how you have 
to do it yourself, this, of the Guru’s working.

481
00:58:03,430 --> 00:58:08,390
You have to work out your Void clearly.

482
00:58:08,390 --> 00:58:16,309
First of all, you have to know that the Void 
catches when you have a wrong type of a guru

483
00:58:16,309 --> 00:58:24,030
– you have had.

484
00:58:24,030 --> 00:58:31,780
You must know about your Guru entirely.

485
00:58:31,780 --> 00:58:37,800
Try to find out the character of your Guru.

486
00:58:37,800 --> 00:58:50,789
Rather difficult, because your Guru is very 
elusive, She’s Mahamaya, not easy to find

487
00:58:50,789 --> 00:58:51,789
out.

488
00:58:51,789 --> 00:59:08,289
She behaves in a very normal way, and sometimes 
you are outwitted.

489
00:59:08,289 --> 00:59:17,619
But you see how in small things also, how 
She behaves, how Her character is expressed,

490
00:59:17,619 --> 00:59:27,170
how Her love is expressed, try to remember 
all that; Her forgiveness.

491
00:59:27,170 --> 00:59:38,680
And then you should know that you have the 
Guru which many people must have desired to

492
00:59:38,680 --> 00:59:45,069
have, which is the Source of all the Gurus.

493
00:59:45,069 --> 01:00:02,170
It is the ardent desire of even Brahma, Vishnu, 
Mahesha to have a Guru like that, and They

494
01:00:02,170 --> 01:00:05,789
must be all jealous of you.

495
01:00:05,789 --> 01:00:07,930
But this Guru is very elusive.

496
01:00:07,930 --> 01:00:18,190
So to improve your Void, say that: “Mother, 
You are our Guru”.

497
01:00:18,190 --> 01:00:25,809
Because of this elusiveness, that fear or 
that awe which is necessary, that respect

498
01:00:25,809 --> 01:00:30,450
which is necessary for the Guru is not established.

499
01:00:30,450 --> 01:00:41,180
Unless and until you develop that awe, complete 
awe within you, your Guru principle won’t

500
01:00:41,180 --> 01:00:42,180
develop.

501
01:00:42,180 --> 01:00:47,970
No liberty is to be taken.

502
01:00:47,970 --> 01:00:54,319
I am telling you Myself, but I am extremely 
elusive.

503
01:00:54,319 --> 01:01:01,760
Next moment I’ll make you laugh and forget 
about it, because I’m testing your freedom

504
01:01:01,760 --> 01:01:04,900
to do it, complete freedom.

505
01:01:04,900 --> 01:01:14,510
I’ll play with you in such a manner that 
you’ll be forgetting every moment that I’m

506
01:01:14,510 --> 01:01:22,289
your Guru, every moment.

507
01:01:22,289 --> 01:01:34,200
So first of all you must find out about your 
own Guru.

508
01:01:34,200 --> 01:01:41,309
Establish Her in your heart.

509
01:01:41,309 --> 01:02:02,030
I mean you have a wonderful Guru otherwise, 
I must say, I wish I had one like that!

510
01:02:02,030 --> 01:02:04,680
And She is desireless and sinless, absolutely 
sinless.

511
01:02:04,680 --> 01:02:07,920
Whatever I do, it’s not a sin for Me.

512
01:02:07,920 --> 01:02:11,450
I can kill anyone, do whatever intrigue or 
do anything.

513
01:02:11,450 --> 01:02:15,039
I really tell you, that’s a fact.

514
01:02:15,039 --> 01:02:26,490
Do anything, I am above sin, but I see to 
it that I do not do anything like that in

515
01:02:26,490 --> 01:02:34,839
your presence, so that you do not get one 
of these things, because that is My quality.

516
01:02:34,839 --> 01:02:49,859
You have a very supreme Guru, no doubt, but 
still you must know that those powers of supremacy

517
01:02:49,859 --> 01:02:52,539
you don’t have.

518
01:02:52,539 --> 01:02:59,849
I am above all these things.

519
01:02:59,849 --> 01:03:04,690
I don’t know what are temptations are, nothing!

520
01:03:04,690 --> 01:03:09,680
I mean, I’ll do whatever I like, it’s 
all My whim.

521
01:03:09,680 --> 01:03:17,250
But despite that, I have made Myself very 
normal, and because I must appear before you

522
01:03:17,250 --> 01:03:23,160
in such a manner that you understand what 
is the Statutes.

523
01:03:23,160 --> 01:03:28,799
For Me there are no Statutes.

524
01:03:28,799 --> 01:03:32,990
I make all the Statutes, isn’t it?

525
01:03:32,990 --> 01:03:38,890
Because of you I do all these things and teach 
you every small, small thing, because you

526
01:03:38,890 --> 01:03:41,079
are still children.

527
01:03:41,079 --> 01:03:52,160
In the same way, you must remember that when 
you are talking to other people about Sahaja

528
01:03:52,160 --> 01:03:59,110
Yoga, remember that they will see you all 
the time, and try to understand how far you

529
01:03:59,110 --> 01:04:00,859
are in it.

530
01:04:00,859 --> 01:04:04,359
As I understand you, you try to understand 
them.

531
01:04:04,359 --> 01:04:09,269
As I love you, you try to love them.

532
01:04:09,269 --> 01:04:25,230
I definitely love you, no doubt, but I am 
Nirmama, I am beyond love: it’s a different

533
01:04:25,230 --> 01:04:28,980
state altogether.

534
01:04:28,980 --> 01:04:44,089
Under these circumstances you are better off, 
much better off, because no guru ever goes

535
01:04:44,089 --> 01:04:50,990
to that extent.

536
01:04:50,990 --> 01:04:55,740
Apart from that I am the Source of all the 
shaktis, of all the powers.

537
01:04:55,740 --> 01:05:00,680
So you can have all the powers from Me, whatever 
you like.

538
01:05:00,680 --> 01:05:07,509
I am desireless, but whatever desire you have 
will be fulfilled.

539
01:05:07,509 --> 01:05:15,119
Even about Me you have to desire, look at 
that: how much I am bound by you.

540
01:05:15,119 --> 01:05:21,950
Unless and until you desire My good health, 
I’ll have bad health; it is to that extent.

541
01:05:21,950 --> 01:05:30,710
But to Me, what is bad health and good health?

542
01:05:30,710 --> 01:05:37,670
And under these beautiful conditions you should 
really prosper so well.

543
01:05:37,670 --> 01:05:40,950
There should be no problem for you to be gurus.

544
01:05:40,950 --> 01:05:45,300
Now, the Void is to be established.

545
01:05:45,300 --> 01:05:55,849
First of all you must know your Guru, and 
She is on every Chakra working – imagine!

546
01:05:55,849 --> 01:06:02,960
What a tremendous Guru you have!

547
01:06:02,960 --> 01:06:08,319
With that you’ll feel the confidence.

548
01:06:08,319 --> 01:06:15,019
And because it is such a tremendous Guru, 
everybody is getting Realization so easily.

549
01:06:15,019 --> 01:06:27,069
If you go to a rich man, for him he’s not 
going to give you two “p’s”.

550
01:06:27,069 --> 01:06:35,910
Because She’s so powerful, you are getting 
your powers just like that.

551
01:06:35,910 --> 01:06:48,049
So you have to feel very happy about it, extremely 
happy and beautiful that you have got all

552
01:06:48,049 --> 01:06:49,049
these powers.

553
01:06:49,049 --> 01:06:54,329
At least, those who have been in Sahaja Yoga 
will know this, for some time; those who have

554
01:06:54,329 --> 01:07:02,029
come for the first time may be little bit 
puzzled with My lecture.

555
01:07:02,029 --> 01:07:07,569
All of you know, all of you know for definite 
what it is.

556
01:07:07,569 --> 01:07:20,000
So to understand your own Guru power, you 
must know Who is your Guru: Sakshat Adi Shakti!

557
01:07:20,000 --> 01:07:27,589
Oh God, it’s too much!

558
01:07:27,589 --> 01:07:33,660
Then establish your Void.

559
01:07:33,660 --> 01:07:42,130
A guru does not bend his head before anybody 
else, and specially My disciples.

560
01:07:42,130 --> 01:07:48,450
Except for mothers and sisters and, you see, 
in some relationship if it is so, so you bow

561
01:07:48,450 --> 01:07:52,869
to that.

562
01:07:52,869 --> 01:08:08,420
But they do not bow to anybody else.

563
01:08:08,420 --> 01:08:20,710
And secondly, you must know that your Guru 
has been the Mother of very great people.

564
01:08:20,710 --> 01:08:42,170
The thought of them itself should establish 
your Guru tattwa.

565
01:08:42,170 --> 01:08:48,090
What tremendous Sons I have had, what great 
Personalities.

566
01:08:48,090 --> 01:09:00,840
No words can describe them, and so many of 
them, one after another.

567
01:09:00,840 --> 01:09:07,400
And you are in the same tradition, My disciples.

568
01:09:07,400 --> 01:09:10,960
Keep them as your ideals.

569
01:09:10,960 --> 01:09:14,530
Try to follow them.

570
01:09:14,530 --> 01:09:28,330
Read about them, understand them, what they 
have said, how they have achieved such heights.

571
01:09:28,330 --> 01:09:33,260
Recognize them, respect them.

572
01:09:33,260 --> 01:09:36,220
You will establish your Guru tattwa.

573
01:09:36,220 --> 01:09:39,400
Imbibe all the Statutes within you, and be 
proud about it.

574
01:09:39,400 --> 01:09:43,170
Don’t be misguided by what people are talking, 
multitudes are talking.

575
01:09:43,170 --> 01:09:47,330
We are going to pull the whole multitude towards 
ourselves.

576
01:09:47,330 --> 01:09:58,950
First of all let us establish our weight, 
the gravity.

577
01:09:58,950 --> 01:10:12,800
As Mother Earth keeps everybody pulling towards 
Earth, we’ll be pulling all of them to ourselves.

578
01:10:12,800 --> 01:10:29,960
Today all of you must, within yourself to 
your Spirit, promise that you will be a guru,

579
01:10:29,960 --> 01:10:34,090
worthy of your Mother.

580
01:10:34,090 --> 01:10:41,120
May God bless you.

581
01:10:41,120 --> 01:10:49,790
(Now for people who have come for the first 
time, they should know that Puja is a thing

582
01:10:49,790 --> 01:10:51,070
